Byte and Binary Sizes:
Bit                   #  0 or 1
Byte                  #  8 bits
Word                  #  2 Bytes
DWord                 #  2 words


lowest address <-------------> highest address # Endianness. X-end-first.
least sig      <little endian>        most sig # Endianness
most  sig      <big    endian>       least sig # Endianness
